# Fried Fish


## Ingredients

* whiting/filted fish
* garlic
* butter
* pepper
* salt
* garlic powder
* lemon

## Method

1. High heat generous oil, butter and garlic.
2. Add fish and fry till edges brown.
3. Add garlic powder, salt, pepper, squeeze plenty of lemon.

## Notes
